Bank of America-Merrill India’s Sonthalia Quits, Reuters Says

-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 
2011-03-04T11:24:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/bank-of-america-merrill-india-s-sonthalia-quits-reuters-says.html
Saurabh Sonthalia is quitting as
Indian-based head of Bank of America-Merrill Lynch’s global
capital markets, Reuters reported, citing two people with
knowledge of the move.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Peterson at 
 cpeterson@bloomberg.net  